---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="DFOS Protocol"
  description="Ed25519 signed chains, content-addressed proofs, W3C DIDs. Verifiable identity and content without trusting the platform."
>
  <main>
    <header>
      <h1>DFOS Protocol</h1>
      <p>
        Ed25519 signed chains. Content-addressed proofs. W3C DIDs. Verifiable identity and content
        — without trusting the platform, without accessing the database, without platform-specific
        tooling.
      </p>
      <p class="tagline">The proof is public. The content is private.</p>
    </header>

    <hr />

    <h2>Specifications</h2>
    <nav class="landing-nav">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/spec">Protocol Specification</a>
          <span class="dim">
            — the core protocol: Ed25519 identity chains, content chains, JWS envelopes,
            CID derivation, document envelope, verification rules, and deterministic test vectors
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/did-method">DID Method</a>
          <span class="dim">
            — W3C DID method specification for <code>did:dfos</code>: self-certifying,
            transport-agnostic decentralized identifiers
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <h2>Ecosystem</h2>
    <p class="dim">
      Standard components that build on the protocol — independent specifications for content
      types and chain storage that work together but can be adopted separately.
    </p>
    <nav class="landing-nav">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/content-model">Content Model</a>
          <span class="dim">
            — standard JSON Schema content types (post, profile) for the document envelope
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/registry-api">Registry API</a>
          <span class="dim">
            — HTTP API for chain submission, identity resolution, and operation retrieval
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <h2>Resources</h2>
    <nav class="landing-nav">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://schemas.dfos.com">schemas.dfos.com</a>
          <span class="dim"> — hosted JSON Schema definitions</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@metalabel/dfos-protocol">npm</a>
          <span class="dim"> — @metalabel/dfos-protocol</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/metalabel/dfos">GitHub</a>
          <span class="dim"> — metalabel/dfos</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://verify.dfos.com">Chain Verifier</a>
          <span class="dim"> — browser-based chain verification</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://dfos.com">DFOS</a>
          <span class="dim"> — the platform</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <hr />

    <footer>
      <p class="dim">Yancey · Ilya · Brandon · Lena</p>
      <p class="dim"><a href="https://github.com/metalabel/dfos/blob/main/LICENSE">MIT License</a> · 2026</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Base>
